{"tid":2086942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【71行街】唔上街 呢條片聽日就會變成禁片","createTime":"2020-06-30T13:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T11:43:50.000Z","uid":319631,"like":465,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"dba5f2e223d33eccbfcea79db77497d36034700f","tid":2086942,"uid":319631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:30:49.000Z","msg":"2047年，中國對香港實施一國兩制、高度自治、港人治港、現有的資本主義生活方式五十年不變嘅限期。<br />\n<br />\n當2047年嚟到嘅時候，香港會唔會變到全面使用簡體字？會唔會將有異見人士嘅家屬拉去勞改？香港警察已經正式成為皇軍？顛覆國家政權罪會被判處死刑？定會有更加多難以想像嘅情況發生？<br />\n<br />\n2020年嘅香港好似已經上演緊《2047》嘅情節⋯<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">但抗爭仍然繼續進行中。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>本片於2019年5月拍攝完成。</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f6Mdkih9Wjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff6Mdkih9Wjk&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6cb44553\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f6Mdkih9Wjk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條微電影喺2019年5月嘅時候已經拍攝完成，<br />\n因為後期製作嘅原因一直到而家國安法即將來臨之時先上映。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實無他嘅，<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記初心，唔好放棄抗爭。<br />\n未來全部都係未知之數，<br />\n而我地相信黑暗係唔會戰勝光明。<br />\n信念係唔會被任何人剝奪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見。"},{"pid":"cd7270c6835a69de511aac54e5d39e62437a3f5d","tid":2086942,"uid":132355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"聽日見 今宵多珍重"},{"pid":"fb8714835401bfcbe20793e40bf56f769d5b8e3e","tid":2086942,"uid":319631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3e2838bd609947a1e8229199fb17f67385574b","tid":2086942,"uid":90601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hv