By":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得"},{"pid":"cdcbea9e31a7575f6e44b24d88a60c9a38dbb9d4","tid":2086942,"uid":125220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"276d31b2f878e9901a72bf5c2187d76baa9e6827","tid":2086942,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dba5f2e223d33eccbfcea79db77497d36034700f","tid":2086942,"uid":319631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:30:49.000Z","msg":"2047年，中國對香港實施一國兩制、高度自治、港人治港、現有的資本主義生活方式五十年不變嘅限期。<br />\n<br />\n當2047年嚟到嘅時候，香港會唔會變到全面使用簡體字？會唔會將有異見人士嘅家屬拉去勞改？香港警察已經正式成為皇軍？顛覆國家政權罪會被判處死刑？定會有更加多難以想像嘅情況發生？<br />\n<br />\n2020年嘅香港好似已經上演緊《2047》嘅情節⋯<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">但抗爭仍然繼續進行中。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>本片於2019年5月拍攝完成。</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f6Mdkih9Wjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff6Mdkih9Wjk&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6cb44553\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f6Mdkih9Wjk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條微電影喺2019年5月嘅時候已經拍攝完成，<br />\n因為後期製作嘅原因一直到而家國安法即將來臨之時先上映。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實無他嘅，<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記初心，唔好放棄抗爭。<br />\n未來全部都係未知之數，<br />\n而我地相信黑暗係唔會戰勝光明。<br />\n信念係唔會被任何人剝奪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"03e2dd0a905c026d14f1f2378cfb1b55b206e59b","tid":2086942,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:07:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e38a04682bffbeb393deb381eee46f